[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 6.45,
    "text": "[Day in the life of a heart surgeon, Paul Massimiano, MD - cardiac surgeon]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.45,
    "endTime": 9.0,
    "text": "Okay, 6:00 a.m., right on time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.0,
    "endTime": 14.702,
    "text": "It's the story of my professional life, getting to the hospital in the dark and going home in the dark."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.702,
    "endTime": 15.91,
    "text": "We have surgery this morning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.91,
    "endTime": 17.96,
    "text": "We operate most mornings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.96,
    "endTime": 24.945,
    "text": "We're doing open heart surgery on a patient this morning, a minimally invasive mitral valve repair through a little incision in the side."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.32,
    "endTime": 32.78,
    "text": "Ready to go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.78,
    "endTime": 35.51,
    "text": "Patients are nervous before open heart surgery."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.51,
    "endTime": 37.18,
    "text": "It's pretty understandable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.18,
    "endTime": 39.964,
    "text": "But I always tell them the important thing is I'm not nervous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.992,
    "endTime": 44.457,
    "text": "Hey, good morning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.457,
    "endTime": 45.65,
    "text": "Good morning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.65,
    "endTime": 48.478,
    "text": "So you--you showed up, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.978,
    "endTime": 51.02,
    "text": "That's half the battle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.02,
    "endTime": 53.330000000000005,
    "text": "Just showing up is half the battle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.33,
    "endTime": 54.11,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.11,
    "endTime": 56.4,
    "text": "You all set for today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.4,
    "endTime": 58.4,
    "text": "So it's just like we talked about in the office."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.4,
    "endTime": 61.16,
    "text": "We're going to work on fixing your mitral valve."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.16,
    "endTime": 62.388999999999996,
    "text": "Going through the side?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.39,
    "endTime": 65.55,
    "text": "We're going to do a little two inch incision in the side."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.55,
    "endTime": 69.22,
    "text": "Yeah, everything is favorable for that, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.22,
    "endTime": 72.58,
    "text": "So just like we talked about."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.58,
    "endTime": 75.622,
    "text": "So anything go on last night I need to know about?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.622,
    "endTime": 76.99,
    "text": "No major issues, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.99,
    "endTime": 78.399,
    "text": "Yeah, okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.4,
    "endTime": 85.14,
    "text": "Well let's go down to the ICU, and we can review the patients that are there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.14,
    "endTime": 86.62,
    "text": "Okay, good morning, everybody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.62,
    "endTime": 88.24000000000001,
    "text": "What's the plan?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.24,
    "endTime": 94.28999999999999,
    "text": "The plan is if we can get the tubes out today and maybe keep the wires another day, and send him upstairs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.29,
    "endTime": 95.76,
    "text": "Can he go upstairs today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.76,
    "endTime": 96.26,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.26,
    "endTime": 97.48,
    "text": "Okay, very good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.48,
    "endTime": 100.94,
    "text": "Any issues we need to take care of before I go to the operating room?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.94,
    "endTime": 101.259,
    "text": "No, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.26,
    "endTime": 101.76,
    "text": "Nope."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.76,
    "endTime": 102.28,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.28,
    "endTime": 103.27,
    "text": "All righty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.27,
    "endTime": 104.5,
    "text": "All right, have a good day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.5,
    "endTime": 106.51,
    "text": "And I'll catch up with you on the floor after surgery."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.51,
    "endTime": 107.60000000000001,
    "text": "All right, thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.6,
    "endTime": 116.419,
    "text": "The operation is like a well choreographed ballet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.42,
    "endTime": 118.65,
    "text": "Everyone knows their role."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.65,
    "endTime": 126.26,
    "text": "The technicians, and the scrub techs, and the perfusionists who run the heart lung machine, all these people are very sophisticated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.26,
    "endTime": 127.93,
    "text": "They all know exactly what to do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.93,
    "endTime": 130.229,
    "text": "So the environment is very controlled."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.229,
    "endTime": 131.61,
    "text": "It's very pleasant."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.61,
    "endTime": 134.47000000000003,
    "text": "We actually listen to music."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.47,
    "endTime": 138.63,
    "text": "Now the kind of music that we listen to is always a question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.63,
    "endTime": 141.41,
    "text": "If it were up to me, I'd listen to classical music."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.41,
    "endTime": 147.44,
    "text": "But I've got a lot of 20 somethings and 30 somethings in there that if they listen to classical music, they get bored."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.44,
    "endTime": 153.29,
    "text": "So in order to keep them happy, I listen to rap or hip hop and a lot of pop music."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.29,
    "endTime": 159.56,
    "text": "If you do something 1,000 times or 10,000 times, you get the sequence into your mind."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.56,
    "endTime": 167.01500000000001,
    "text": "And then the only thing you have to do is be ready for unexpected circumstances, which in a case like this, would be very, very unusual."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.94,
    "endTime": 178.19,
    "text": "Okay, so I've got these special magnifying lenses on called loops."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.19,
    "endTime": 184.67,
    "text": "And it allows me to see inside a magnified 3.5 times, so everything looks very big and very close."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.67,
    "endTime": 187.60899999999998,
    "text": "And it helps us to evaluate valves and coronary arteries."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.14,
    "endTime": 192.2,
    "text": "Okay, well we're all finished."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.2,
    "endTime": 194.98899999999998,
    "text": "Surgery's over, everything went fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.99,
    "endTime": 199.10000000000002,
    "text": "We were able to fix the patient's valve through a little two inch incision."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.1,
    "endTime": 203.089,
    "text": "He was stable through the whole time, and I'm completely satisfied."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.09,
    "endTime": 206.55,
    "text": "So now let's go give the family the good news."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.55,
    "endTime": 209.69500000000002,
    "text": "Okay, everything went great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.695,
    "endTime": 210.57,
    "text": "Yeah, we're all done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.57,
    "endTime": 212.16,
    "text": "The operation was nice and smooth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.16,
    "endTime": 213.763,
    "text": "Everything went fine, okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.77,
    "endTime": 216.0,
    "text": "The nurses will give you a full briefing on what to expect once you see him in the ICU."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.53,
    "endTime": 218.16,
    "text": "Wonderful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.16,
    "endTime": 218.46,
    "text": "Okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.46,
    "endTime": 219.18,
    "text": "I appreciate that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.18,
    "endTime": 219.6,
    "text": "All righty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.6,
    "endTime": 220.26,
    "text": "Thank you so much, Doctor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.26,
    "endTime": 221.51899999999998,
    "text": "And we'll talk later."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.52,
    "endTime": 223.29000000000002,
    "text": "All righty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.29,
    "endTime": 228.07,
    "text": "Okay, well the first case is over, and had a successful completion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.07,
    "endTime": 229.56,
    "text": "So I'm pretty satisfied."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.56,
    "endTime": 233.4,
    "text": "One thing about cardiac surgery is that every day is a new day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.4,
    "endTime": 234.4,
    "text": "It's exciting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.4,
    "endTime": 238.52,
    "text": "I've never been bored a single day in my entire career."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.52,
    "endTime": 248.03,
    "text": "So all in all, it's a pleasure and it's an honor to operate on patients and be entrusted with their care."
  }
]